    <!-- About Card -->
    <div class="card card-about anim anim-d2">
      <div class="card-label"><span class="label-dot"></span> About</div>
      <p class="about-text">
        I'm a software engineer at <strong>Siemens</strong> and an indie builder obsessed with making AI tools that actually remember. I believe the best developer tools should <strong>compound intelligence</strong> over time, not reset every session.
